sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant FE as Frontend<br/>React SPA
  participant GW as API Gateway<br/>NGINX
  participant AS as Auth Service<br/>JWT + PKCE
  participant US as User Service
  participant OS as Order Service
  participant PS as Payment Service<br/>Stripe
  participant K as Kafka<br/>Event Bus
  participant NS as Notification Svc
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  Note over U,DB: Checkout Flow — Happy Path

  U->>FE: Click "Conferma Ordine"
  activate FE
  FE->>FE: Validate cart locally
  FE->>GW: POST /api/orders {items, address, paymentMethod}
  activate GW
  GW->>AS: Verify JWT token
  activate AS
  AS->>AS: Decode + check expiry
  AS-->>GW: 200 OK {userId: "u_abc123"}
  deactivate AS

  GW->>OS: POST /orders (authenticated)
  activate OS
  OS->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
  activate DB
  OS->>DB: INSERT orders (status=pending)
  OS->>DB: INSERT order_items (qty, price snapshot)
  OS->>DB: UPDATE inventory (reserve stock)
  DB-->>OS: OK — orderId: "ord_789"
  deactivate DB

  OS->>PS: POST /payments/charge {orderId, amount: €127.50, method}
  activate PS
  PS->>PS: Stripe API call
  Note right of PS: 3D Secure may trigger<br/>additional auth step
  PS-->>OS: 200 {paymentId: "pay_xyz", status: "succeeded"}
  deactivate PS

  OS->>DB: UPDATE orders SET status='paid', payment_id='pay_xyz'
  activate DB
  DB-->>OS: OK
  deactivate DB

  OS->>K: Publish OrderPaid {orderId, userId, items, amount}
  activate K
  K-->>OS: ACK (partition 3, offset 48291)
  deactivate K
  OS-->>GW: 201 Created {orderId: "ord_789", status: "paid"}
  deactivate OS
  GW-->>FE: 201 Created
  deactivate GW
  FE-->>U: Redirect to /orders/ord_789 (confirmation page)
  deactivate FE

  Note over K,NS: Async event processing

  K->>NS: Consume OrderPaid event
  activate NS
  NS->>NS: Render email template
  NS->>NS: Send email via SES
  NS->>NS: Send push notification via FCM
  NS-->>K: Commit offset
  deactivate NS

  Note over U,DB: Error Path — Payment Failure

  rect rgb(80, 20, 40)
    U->>FE: Click "Conferma Ordine" (insufficient funds)
    FE->>GW: POST /api/orders {items, address}
    GW->>OS: POST /orders
    OS->>PS: POST /payments/charge
    PS-->>OS: 402 {error: "card_declined", decline_code: "insufficient_funds"}
    OS->>DB: UPDATE orders SET status='payment_failed'
    OS->>K: Publish OrderPaymentFailed {orderId, reason}
    OS-->>GW: 402 Payment Required {error: "Pagamento rifiutato"}
    GW-->>FE: 402
    FE-->>U: Show error toast + retry option
  end
